%vlocity_namespace%__Description__c: The stop loss aggregate attachment point (or "Agg") -- this is the amount that the self-funded employer must pay, for all covered persons, before the stop-loss insurance kicks in.
Name: Stop Loss Aggregate Attachment Point

%vlocity_namespace%__Description__c: Stop Loss Specific attachment point (or "Spec") -- this is the amount that the self-funded employer must pay, per covered person, before the stop-loss insurance kicks in. It's like a per-person deductible that the employer pays.
Name: Stop Loss Specific Attachment Point
